{"lemma":"صَبارَةُ","slug":"صَبارَةُ","root":"ص.ب.ر","root_slug":"ص-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ب-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23681","n23682","n23683","n23687","n23691"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23681","headword_ar":"صَبَارَةٌ","root":"Sbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph:       -A2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaAr~apN","text_ar":"صَبَارَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23682","headword_ar":"صُبَارَةٌ","root":"Sbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArapN","text_ar":"صَبَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibaArapN","text_ar":"صِبَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smooth stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubaArapN","text_ar":"صُبَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies, (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArapN","text_ar":"صَبَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of stone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion of stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of iron."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) A poet says, (S,) namely, El-Aashà, (M,) or 'Amr Ibn-Milkat Et-Tá-ee, addressing 'Amr Ibn-Hind, who had a brother slain, (IB,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"mano muboligN EamorFA biA^an~a Almaro'a lamo yuxolaqo SubaAraho"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in the S; but in the M and TA this verse is given differently, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayobaAna","text_ar":"شَيْبَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~a","text_ar":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the places of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamorFA","text_ar":"عَمْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^an~a","text_ar":"بِاَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and it is said in the M that accord. to one relation the last word is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiyaAraho","text_ar":"صِيَارَهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":",] which, it is added, is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubaArah","text_ar":"صُبَارَه"},{"kind":"text","text":"in meaning;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Who will tell 'Amr,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sheybán, that man was not created stones?"},{"kind":"text","text":"] but IB says that the last word is correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibaAraho","text_ar":"صِبَارَهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"S","text_ar":"ص"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the poet means, man is not stone, that he should patiently endure the like of this: (TA:) [J says,] accord. to one relation, the last word is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaAraho","text_ar":"صَبَارَهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, which is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArN","text_ar":"صَبَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArN","text_ar":"صَبَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being affixed to denote its being a pl. pl., for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaborapN","text_ar":"صَبْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of ↓ signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and he adds,] El-Aashà says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      qubayola AlS~uboHi A^aSowaAtu AlS~abaAri"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) but IB says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArN","text_ar":"صَبَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArapN","text_ar":"صَبَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are not pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaborapN","text_ar":"صَبْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEaAlN","text_ar":"فَعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not a pl. form, but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEaAlN","text_ar":"فِعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaArN","text_ar":"حِجَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAlN","text_ar":"جِبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [and it is said that] the verse from which this is cited is not by El-Aashà, and is correctly and completely as follows:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"kaA^an~a taran~uma AlhaAjaAti fiyhaA\n                      \n                     \n                        qubayola AlS~uboHi A^aSowaAtu AlS~iyaAri"},{"kind":"text","text":"by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlSyAr","text_ar":"الصيار"},{"kind":"text","text":"being meant the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sanoj","text_ar":"صَنْج"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TS, K, TA,) the stringed instrument thus called: (TS, TA:)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1646},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to the reading given in the S, the verse means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As though the croaking of the frogs in it, a little before daybreak, were the sounds of"},{"kind":"text","text":"falling"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and this is correct. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiyrN","text_ar":"صَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","TA","IB","TS"]},{"entry_id":"n23683","headword_ar":"صِبَارَةٌ","root":"Sbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23687","headword_ar":"صَبَارَّةٌ","root":"Sbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [respecting the form of which see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAr~apN","text_ar":"حَمَارَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (S, M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaArapN","text_ar":"صَبَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", without teshdeed, (Lh, M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaborapN","text_ar":"صَبْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intenseness of the cold"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) of winter: (S, M:) and [in an absolute sense]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intenseness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of cold: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaborapN","text_ar":"صَبْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of winter; (K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SawobarapN","text_ar":"صَوْبَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","Lh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n23691","headword_ar":"صَبَّارَةٌ","root":"Sbr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rugged ground, rising above the adjacent part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts, and hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is no herbage, and which produces none:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u","text_ar":"اُمُّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sab~aAri","text_ar":"صَبَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabirN","text_ar":"صَبِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}